    <description>
	XFShapeView for Xamarin.Forms provides a custom ContentView allowing you to draw customizable shapes in Android and iOS apps.
	
	Support for box, rounded box, circle, oval and star shapes. As this library is based on a ContentView, you can easily add any view/layout to any shape.
	
	Sample available on GitHub (https://github.com/vincentgury/XFShapeView)
	</description>
	<summary>Cross platform shape view for Xamarin.Forms (iOS &amp; Android)</summary>
